。1月18日當地時間9點，一輛載滿炸彈的車輛衝進聯合作戰行動的基地<Ref name="nytimes">
{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/18/world/africa/suicide-attack-at-military-camp-in-mali-kills-scores.html|title=Suicide Attack at Military Camp in Mali Kills Scores|publisher=The New York Times|date=18 January 2017|accessdate=19 January 2017|archive-date=2017-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120070200/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/18/world/africa/suicide-attack-at-military-camp-in-mali-kills-scores.html|dead-url=no}}
</ref>，該基地為馬利軍隊及民兵駐紮<Ref name="wpost">{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/truck-bomb-kills-50-pro-government-fighters-in-northern-mali/2017/01/18/a5b597f0-dd79-11e6-ad42-f3375f271c9c_story.html?utm_term=.b9f58b2af911|title=Truck bomb kills at least 60, including army troops, in northern Mali |publisher=The Washington Post|date=18 January 2017|accessdate=19 January 2017}}</ref>。

